channel.title: Thinking of starting my old ps up again. Cant find file. HELP!
channel.description:
Hey, I used to be on this site a lot and I constructed a private server by the name of LanthusScape. I eventually stopped and shut down the server, I also left this site at that time. Now I want to start it up again but when I search the term "Lanthus" or "LanthusScape" it comes up with posts before and after I released my source. But never anything that could link to it. Could anybody tell me why this is? Did they reset the downloads section or do posts just get deleted after a certain time?
EDIT: Just went through all my posts. I did find a link to the server client but it brought me to an invalid url error. It's like it just disappeared.
